This version dated Thu Sep 20 2001

ParaSails installation

0. Look at the manual: manual.ps
1. Modify makefile for your local environment.  MPI and LAPACK/BLAS or ESSL 
   libraries are required.
2. Type "make"
3. Type "make driver"
4. Modify testscript for running parallel programs in your local environment.
5. Run the testscript.  The testscript compares the computations with 
   precomputed approximate inverses.  There may be minor differences
   depending on the arithmetic of your machine.

Send questions, comments, and support requests to Edmond Chow, echow@llnl.gov
